            11 => 
            array (
                'id' => 34,
                'uuid' => 'e4e38aea-0856-441a-860a-36d16f52d1ae',
                'news_id' => 34,
                'language_id' => 1,
                'category_id' => 11,
                'sub_category_id' => 42,
                'encode_title' => 'shakil-makes-history-as-youngest-sea-to-summit-everest-conqueror',
                'seo_title' => NULL,
                'stitle' => 'Sea to Summit Everest',
                'title' => 'Shakil makes history as youngest ‘Sea to Summit Everest’ conqueror',
                'news' => '<p><span style="font-family:Georgia,serif;"><span style="font-size:16px;">In a truly awe-inspiring feat of human endurance, willpower, and national pride, <strong>Shakil</strong>, born on <strong>April 17, 1994</strong>, has made history by becoming the <strong>youngest and fastest individual to complete the legendary &lsquo;Sea to Summit Everest&rsquo; challenge</strong>. Over the course of <strong>90 relentless days</strong>, he traveled an extraordinary distance of <strong>1,300 kilometers</strong>, starting from sea level and pushing onward until he reached the <strong>summit of Mount Everest</strong>, the highest point on Earth at <strong>8,848.86 meters</strong>. This rare expedition, known for its immense physical and psychological demands, requires athletes to endure punishing terrain, extreme altitude, unpredictable weather, and the constant threat of exhaustion or injury.</span></span></p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><span style="font-family:Georgia,serif;"><span style="font-size:16px;">Shakil&rsquo;s journey wasn&#39;t just a personal conquest&mdash;it is a <strong>symbolic victory for his country</strong>, putting it on the global map for adventure and high-altitude achievements. His success reflects <strong>grit, precise planning, and relentless preparation</strong>, combining long-distance endurance trekking, elite-level climbing, and sheer mental strength. From <strong>humid coastal regions</strong>, through <strong>dense forests and rocky trails</strong>, across <strong>snow-covered landscapes</strong>, and finally to the <strong>icy slopes of Everest</strong>, Shakil&rsquo;s accomplishment is nothing short of heroic.</span></span></p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<h3><span style="font-family:Georgia,serif;"><span style="font-size:20px;">Highlights of Shakil&#39;s Historic Journey:</span></span></h3>

<ul>
<li>
<p><span style="font-family:Georgia,serif;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong>1,300 km covered on foot and climb</strong> from sea level to Everest&rsquo;s peak</span></span></p>
</li>
<li>
<p><span style="font-family:Georgia,serif;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong>90 days of non-stop effort</strong>, crossing multiple terrain zones</span></span></p>
</li>
<li>
<p><span style="font-family:Georgia,serif;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong>T</strong></span><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong>echnical climbs, glacial crossings, and high-altitude acclimatization</strong></span></span></p>
</li>
<li>
<p><span style="font-family:Georgia,serif;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong>Recognition as the youngest and fastest &lsquo;Sea to Summit Everest&rsquo; finisher</strong></span></span></p>
</li>
<li>
<p><span style="font-family:Georgia,serif;"><span style="font-size:16px;">&nbsp;<strong>landmark achievement for his nation</strong>, inspiring youth and mountaineers alike</span></span></p>
</li>
</ul>

<p><span style="font-family:Georgia,serif;"><span style="font-size:16px;">This unprecedented triumph now stands as a <strong>beacon of inspiration</strong> for aspiring adventurers across the world. Shakil&rsquo;s journey proves that with <strong>vision, resilience, and courage</strong>, even the most extreme goals are within reach. His legacy will not only be remembered in mountaineering history but will continue to motivate generations to come.</span></span></p>',
                'image' => '2SNXBiMG3YuiIvYGiDbhztU8LmbmVTFIsCqOn2CR.jpg',
