<p data-end="1799" data-start="1584"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:Georgia,serif;">The 2027 edition is more than a tournament&mdash;it&#39;s an opportunity for <strong data-end="1688" data-start="1651">Africa to shine on a global stage</strong>, blending <strong data-end="1720" data-start="1699">sports excellence</strong> with <strong data-end="1747" data-start="1726">cultural richness</strong> and redefining the future of international cricket.</span></span></p>',
