                'encode_title' => 'police-rescue-two-abducted-children-in-narayanganj-three-arrested',
                'seo_title' => NULL,
                'stitle' => NULL,
                'title' => 'Police Rescue Two Abducted Children in Narayanganj; Three Arrested',
                'news' => '<p data-end="2391" data-start="2158">Narayanganj district police successfully rescued <strong data-end="2232" data-start="2207">two abducted children</strong> from a rented house in <strong data-end="2268" data-start="2256">Fatullah</strong> on Saturday night, ending a 48-hour search operation that began after a missing person report was filed by a local family.</p>

<p data-end="2644" data-start="2393">The children &mdash; <strong data-end="2421" data-start="2408">Riyad (9)</strong> and <strong data-end="2439" data-start="2426">Siam (11)</strong> &mdash; went missing from their neighborhood in <strong data-end="2491" data-start="2482">Pagla</strong> on Thursday afternoon while returning from madrasa. Family members received a <strong data-end="2600" data-start="2570">ransom demand of Tk 5 lakh</strong> the next morning via anonymous phone calls.</p>

<h3 data-end="2691" data-start="2646">High-Tech Surveillance Led to Arrests</h3>

<p data-end="2995" data-start="2693">Acting on digital intelligence and mobile tracking, a team from the Detective Branch (DB) raided a single-story building in Fatullah where the children were being held. Three suspects &mdash; identified as <strong data-end="2918" data-start="2893">Jahangir Hossain (45)</strong>, <strong data-end="2939" data-start="2920">Razu Ahmed (29)</strong>, and <strong data-end="2965" data-start="2945">Shila Begum (35)</strong> &mdash; were arrested at the scene.</p>

<p data-end="3168" data-start="2997">&ldquo;We rescued the children unharmed and recovered mobile phones, SIM cards, and two toy pistols used to threaten them,&rdquo; said <strong data-end="3167" data-start="3120">Superintendent of Police (SP) Zakir Hossain</strong>.</p>

<p data-end="3168" data-start="2997">&nbsp;</p>

<hr data-end="3173" data-start="3170" />
<h3 data-end="3204" data-start="3175">&nbsp;</h3>

<h3 data-end="3204" data-start="3175">Criminal Charges Filed</h3>

<p data-end="3377" data-start="3206">The suspects have been charged under the <strong data-end="3290" data-start="3247">Kidnapping and Extortion Prevention Act</strong>, and police say the group may be linked to other child abduction attempts in the area.</p>

<p data-end="3478" data-start="3379">&ldquo;This was a planned crime. We&rsquo;re investigating whether it&rsquo;s part of a larger ring,&rdquo; SP Zakir added.</p>

<p data-end="3584" data-start="3480">The rescued children have been reunited with their families and are undergoing psychological counseling.</p>

<hr data-end="3589" data-start="3586" />
