<td data-col-size="sm" data-end="1684" data-start="1641"><span style="font-family:Georgia,serif;"><span style="font-size:16px;">Floods, droughts, labor shortages</span></span></td>
</tr>
<tr data-end="1796" data-start="1685">
<td data-col-size="sm" data-end="1708" data-start="1685"><span style="font-family:Georgia,serif;"><span style="font-size:16px;">Dairy Products</span></span></td>
<td data-col-size="sm" data-end="1753" data-start="1708"><span style="font-family:Georgia,serif;"><span style="font-size:16px;">+15%</span></span></td>
<td data-col-size="sm" data-end="1796" data-start="1753"><span style="font-family:Georgia,serif;"><span style="font-size:16px;">High feed prices, energy costs</span></span></td>
</tr>
<tr data-end="1908" data-start="1797">
