<p><span style="font-size:12px;"><span style="font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif;"><strong data-end="2130" data-start="2113">Key Takeaway:</strong> The South and West have seen consistent growth due to warmer climates, job markets, and immigration hubs (e.g., Texas, Florida, California).</span></span></p>
