                'title' => 'The United States has long been known as a nation of immigrants and diversity',
                'news' => '<p data-end="812" data-start="427"><span style="font-size:14px;">The United States has long been known as a nation of immigrants and diversity. Over the last century, significant demographic changes have occurred due to immigration patterns, birth rates, cultural shifts, and changing social values. This report outlines how the racial, regional, religious, and national origin composition of the U.S. population has evolved &mdash; and where it&rsquo;s heading.</span></p>

<p data-end="812" data-start="427">&nbsp;</p>

